headline: China Reports First Fatality From New Virus
abstract: The coronavirus, which surfaced in the city of Wuhan, has put the region on alert, but there is no evidence that it can spread among humans.
lead_paragraph: HONG KONG â€” Chinese state media on Saturday reported the first known death from a new virus that has infected dozens of people in China and set off worries across Asia.
